New Methods: (33 Methods)
- Sensor - getStatus(sensor_id) | Retrieves status for sensor (Online/Offline)
- Sensor - setStatus(sensor_id,status) | Set status for sensor (Online/Offline)
- Sensor - getName(sensor_id) | Retrieves sensor name
- Sensor - getReadings(sensor_id,dataType,timeStart,timeEnd) | Retrieves all readings between timeStart and timeEnd in epoch time of type dataType (temp, pressure, etc). This will allow creating the graphs.
- Sensor - getLastReading(sensor_id,dataType) | Retrieves the last reading for dataType from a sensor
- Sensor - getLastUpdated(sensor_id) | Retrieves the time in minutes since the last update
- Sensor - countOnline(user_id) | Returns amount of online sensors for a user
- Sensor - countOffline(user_id) | Returns amount of offline sensors for a user
- Alert - getSensor(alert_id) | Returns the sensor_id associated with the alert
- User - updateUser(user_id,name,email,phone_number,company_name) | Update user's basic information
- User - getAlerts(user_id) | Returns a list of alerts sent to the user
- User - getEmail(user_id) | Get email for a user
- User - getName(user_id) | Get name for a user
- User - getCompanyName(user_id) | Get company name for a user
- User - getPhoneNumber(user_id) | Get phone number for a user
- User - getTimeZone(user_id) | Get timezone for a user
- User - setTimeZone(user_id,timezone) | Set timezone for a user
- User - updatePassword(user_id,old_password,new_password) | Update password for user
- User - addCard(user_id,cardNumber,nameOnCard,cardExpiration,cvc,address1,address2,city,state,country,zip) | Add a card for a user
- User - updateCard(user_id,card_id,cardNumber,nameOnCard,cardExpiration,cvc,address1,address2,city,state,country,zip) | Update a card for a user
- User - deleteCard(user_id,card_id) | Delete a card for a user
- User - getActiveCard(user_id) | Get the active card for a user
- User - setActiveCard(user_id,card_id) | Set the active card for a user
- User - getCards(user_id) | Get all cards on file for a user
- User - createBill(user_id,billing_date,amount) | Create a bill for a user
- User - updateBill(user_id,bill_id,status) | Update the status of a bill for a user
- User - deleteBill(user_id,bill_id) | Delete a bill for a user
- User - getBills(user_id) | Get all bills for a user
- User - addAlarmRecipient(user_id,name,email) | Add an alarm recipient for user
- User - deleteAlarmRecipient(user_id,alarm_recipient_id) | Delete an alarm recipient for a user
- User - getAlarmRecipients(user_id) | Get all alarm recipients for user
- User - getAlarmRecipientStatus(user_id,alarm_recipient_id) | Get enabled (true or false) for alarm recipient for a user
- User - setAlarmRecipientStatus(user_id,alarm_recipient_id,enabled) | Set enabled (true or false) for alarm recipient for a user